This year's lecture centred on the theme of “Constitutionalism is an Instrument for Transformation”. JOHANNESBURG – Chief Justice Mogoeng Mogoeng on Saturday delivered the 17th Annual Nelson Mandela Lecture at the University of Johannesburg's Soweto Campus. This year's lecture centred on the theme of “Constitutionalism as an Instrument for Transformation”. WATCH: Chief justice delivers annual Nelson Mandela Lecture 